The '''Great Desert of Dathomir''' was a massive desert on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]] that measured eighty kilometers long. This region was home to the [[Blue Desert People]] who were members of the [[Kwi]] species.<ref name="CoPL">''[[The Courtship of Princess Leia]]''</ref>

